{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342630/extras/GifNum1.gif?t=1734289911\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Welcome to Sandhill</i></strong><i>, where survival lurks in the shadows. You awaken in darkness, disoriented, with only the distant echoes of alarms and the dim beam of a flashlight to guide you. Armed with nothing but your wits, you must navigate the treacherous, haunting corridors of Sandhill\u2019s forgotten tunnels\u2014each corner harboring secrets and the tormented shadows of those who fell victim to gruesome experiments.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>In this atmospheric horror adventure, every step is a new puzzle, every shadow a potential threat. Unravel the mysteries hidden within these depths, piece together clues, and follow the message from an old friend, who may hold the key to your escape\u2014or your doom. But beware: the darkness is alive, and it remembers.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342630/extras/GifNum2.gif?t=1734289911\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Features:</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Explore the legendary, ominous tunnels of Sandhill, steeped in secrets and haunted by restless souls.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Solve intricate puzzles to unlock new areas and reveal the horrifying past.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Face dangers lurking in the shadows as you try to escape creatures born from twisted experiments.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Uncover the truth behind a cryptic message that may just lead to salvation\u2026 or seal your fate.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">FPS/TPS Gameplay</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"n